Program: Discovery
Title: Monstrous Science - monsters fact and fiction
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jryh4
Last Broadcast Date: 03 September 2003
Giants, fact and fiction;dinosaurs, giant squids, Big Foot and the Loch Ness Monster. In the first of the four programmes presenter Andrew Luck-Baker investigates the giants of earth's geological history and how such monsters functioned. Looking at huge dinosaurs, giant squids, Big Foot and the Loch Ness Monster. Show less